%% Scania — Asset selection via live FMAT fetch (POC, no caching — ADR-002)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Fleet Customer
    participant Yves as Yves (Asset UI)
    participant Zed as Zed (ScaniaFmatAsset)
    participant Client as FMAT Client
    participant FMAT as FMAT (Fleet Mgmt)

    Note over User,FMAT: Assets are fetched live on every page load — no Spryker persistence for POC (ADR-002)
    User->>Yves: Open "My Fleet" (page N)
    Yves->>Zed: getAssets(customerId, page)
    Zed->>Client: fetchAssets(customerRef, page, pageSize)
    Client->>FMAT: GET /assets?customer=…&page=N (REST, sync)
    alt FMAT responds
        FMAT-->>Client: Paginated vehicle list (VIN, model, …)
        Client-->>Zed: AssetTransfer collection
        Zed-->>Yves: Assets + pagination
        Yves-->>User: Render paginated fleet list
        User->>Yves: Select a vehicle
        Yves-->>User: Proceed to service catalog (see service-browse-select)
    else FMAT unavailable
        FMAT-->>Client: Error / timeout
        Note right of Client: POC — surface exception (graceful<br/>error handling is Future scope)
        Client-->>Yves: Exception
    end
